name: In The Middle Of NWHR
description: Yeah, blast from the past, I rlly love this piece and is one of my personal faves. Emotional struggle and bad relationship with my family resulted in constant searching of my happy place. this was the begginig. With this piece I got featured on advancedphotoshop facebook page with this one heres wht thy wrote Advanced Photoshop magazine Love this image from our Gallery, In the Middle of Nowhere by Nikola Milutinovic. Looks like a Photoshop riff on JMW Turner's Fighting Temeraire. We're pretty sure old Turner would have rocked the new Blur filters in CC.
